title: Barley Crop for Great Britain
notes:
Data For 1884-1905 Were Published In Original Source As Imperial Bushels; Data For 1906-1938 Were Published As Quarters And Converted To Imperial Bushels By Dividing By Eight. Data Exclude Ireland. Source: Ministry Of Agriculture And Fisheries, Agricultural Statistics.

This NBER data series a01020 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
